Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.66,0:03:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.37,0:03:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.51,0:03:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.71,0:03:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在房間 如果晚餐好了就叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.49,0:03:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近阿優都不太跟我玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行那樣就是瀆職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.71,0:03:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶誕節~耶誕節~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.21,0:03:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常棒的耶誕節~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.73,0:03:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.53,0:03:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌 這是真的火雞嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.91,0:03:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我用Sylpheed飛過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.74,0:03:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美國的肯塔基州
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.69,0:03:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從養殖火雞世界第一的\N韓塔森先生的農場直接拿過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.12,0:04:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美…美國？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.55,0:04:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這個聖誕樹呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.41,0:04:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是從芬蘭的得加魯斯地區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.52,0:04:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受裝飾聖誕樹世界第一的\N漢奴格卡聶先生的特訓之後回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這個樅樹也是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.92,0:04:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我一起帶回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.91,0:04:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的幹勁十足呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.07,0:04:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你真的很期待耶誕節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.80,0:04:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.08,0:04:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 阿優\N你難道不期待嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.03,0:04:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.85,0:04:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到麻幌高興我也變得很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.00,0:04:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這樣不就不是單純的\N因為耶誕節而高興了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.81,0:04:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我真的看起來這麼的高興嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.83,0:04:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是高興也不是件壞事啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.39,0:04:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以我的立場 如果沒有先讓阿優高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而只顧讓自己高興的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不介意的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.58,0:05:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我該去買點東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.65,0:05:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和 怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.59,0:05:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了聖誕花圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.34,0:05:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.49,0:05:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我好像搞錯了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.37,0:05:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在外面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.50,0:05:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.08,0:05:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然是努力做出來的就沒必要藏起來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 美奈和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很努力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.68,0:05:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用來避邪也許不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.50,0:05:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.19,0:05:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-對不起 對不起 對不起\N-阿優 你還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.85,0:05:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.24,0:05:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們傍晚就會回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.65,0:06:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.49,0:06:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就只剩下麻幌一個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.37,0:06:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.47,0:06:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是濱口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.30,0:06:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要找阿優的話他剛剛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.10,0:06:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.14,0:06:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.93,0:06:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有話想對你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.30,0:06:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.06,0:06:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.90,0:06:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,街上有這麼稀奇嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.94,0:06:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我是第一次到這麼熱鬧的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.26,0:07:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真心的Merry X'mas
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.53,0:07:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.18,0:07:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.82,0:07:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個味道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.98,0:07:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 你在下北的芬聶修行過對吧\Nps.下北:日本青森縣的一個半島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.55,0:07:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個巧克力慕斯滑溜的口感\N一定是那家店直接傳授的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.70,0:07:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是比起本店還是需要多多磨練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.46,0:07:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴 要走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.17,0:07:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不一起走會變成迷途羔羊喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.36,0:07:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.05,0:07:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小凜買了什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.75,0:07:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個當然是秘密吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.53,0:07:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到交換禮物的時候才能知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴什麼都沒買嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.12,0:08:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.02,0:08:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不能叫他啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為只有他們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.79,0:08:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是約會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.65,0:08:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太大聲了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在那裏做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師你為什麼會在這裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.29,0:08:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為到了假日行為容易出軌的學生太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.62,0:08:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我跟流河老師在巡邏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.44,0:08:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.29,0:08:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 綜合各種線索思考\N聖誕老人並不存在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.70,0:08:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是大人居然還相信有聖誕老人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.58,0:08:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 哪有這種事~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也稍微有點感覺到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.63,0:08:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-一定有聖誕老人的啦\N-我到底在做什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.96,0:08:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 其實是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們並沒有跟蹤你們啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.17,0:08:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.40,0:08:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她要去選禮物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.59,0:08:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼知道她有來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禮物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.44,0:09:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.51,0:09:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道買了些什麼的話\N交換的時候就很無聊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.97,0:09:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和她還沒有買好啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.95,0:09:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好像一直在考慮的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.41,0:09:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交換禮物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.19,0:09:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家聚在一起很可疑喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.59,0:09:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不可疑啦…老師你想太多…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.63,0:09:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不可疑啦…老師你想太多…\N-之前好像也有類似這樣的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.88,0:09:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}『未滿18歲禁止觀賞所以無法描繪』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.88,0:09:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會是我所想像的那樣嗎？\N(啊~不能這樣~美裏同學~)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.81,0:09:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(不行不行~)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師的行為才不太正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.31,0:09:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是常常這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.66,0:09:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先溜了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.34,0:09:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和喜歡的東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.29,0:09:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 我想麻幌一定能夠給我一些意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.75,0:09:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.46,0:09:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.70,0:10:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和在學校一直都很老實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且老是道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.65,0:10:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我很在意…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我沒什麼奇怪的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.45,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是單純的想讓她高興一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濱口你真是溫柔呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.07,0:10:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管送什麼東西 只要有那份心意的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想美奈和一定會高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.63,0:10:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.59,0:10:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我跟美奈和也認識不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.37,0:10:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我說了什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.51,0:10:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「認識不久」什麼的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.23,0:10:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽錯了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.98,0:10:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.48,0:10:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打擾你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那下次見…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 下次見…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好危險喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.57,0:10:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 為什麼濱口他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會這樣在意美奈和的事呢？
