Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.85,0:17:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用放在心上啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.35,0:17:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼貴重的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.89,0:17:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小時候啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相當的皮呢
